WHELAN SECURITY IS NOW HIRING!! Immediate FT/PT/DAY/GRAVE/SWING Shifts openings available at a National Client in the area!<br>
<br>
Come down to our area branch office located at 655 N. Central Ave. Suite 1706, Glendale, CA 91203 from 10:00am to 4:00pm THIS Thursday. We are waiting to meet you! Walk-ins welcome!!<br>
<br>
PLEASE COME READY TO INTERVIEW WITH RESUME IN HAND AND APPLY ONLINE BEFOREHAND!<br>
<br>
WE ARE SEARCHING FOR SOLID SECURITY PROFESSIONALS WHO HAVE EXPERIENCE. WE OFFER FT/PT SHIFTS ALONG WITH A COMPREHENSIVE BENEFITS PACKAGE FOR FT EMPLOYEES.<br>
<br>
<br>
Why Whelan?<br>
Whelan Security is one of the largest contract security companies in the industry with many exciting career opportunities nationwide. Whelan offers our team members a generous compensation and benefits package, numerous career development and advancement opportunities as well as the historical stability and confidence of working for a company that has been in business since 1949. We can help you achieve your professional goals and provide you with the tools necessary to be successful in this industry. All YOU need is a strong work ethic and a passion to provide exceptional customer service, safety and security.<br>
<br>
Apply now and become part of our world class security team!<br>
<br>
Our security positions are ideal for:<br>
- Former, transitioning and military reserve personnel<br>
- Former and future law enforcement officers<br>
- Hospitality and customer service professionals<br>
- College students<br>
- Retirees<br>
<br>
At Whelan we offer:<br>
- Competitive wages ranging $12.80-$14.70/hr<br>
- Medical Benefits<br>
- Paid Vacations<br>
- 401 (k) with employer matching<br>
- Free Uniforms<br>
<br>
Successful candidates must meet the following requirements: <br>
- Legally authorized to work in the United States<br>
- At least 21 years of age or older as required by applicable law or contractual requirements<br>
- Demonstrate a stable work history<br>
- Pass an extensive background screening which includes, but is not limited to, criminal background checks (local, state and federal), drug test, aptitude tests, skills assessment, interviews, and personality profile (behavioral assessment)<br>
- Valid CA guard card<br>
-Valid CA driver's license<br>
<br>
Candidates must meet the following educational requirements: <br>
- Possess at least a high school education or equivalent (GED)<br>
<br>
Apply Now!<br>
<br>
If you have an interest in joining a leader in the contract security industry and would like to work at one or more of our outstanding client locations in the Los Angeles, CA area -- APPLY NOW!<br>
<br>
To Apply: <br>
Please go to our website www.greatsecurityofficers.com or www.whelansecurity.com and apply to requisition #4649BR in the Southern California location.<br>
<br>
PLEASE NOTE WE WILL ONLY CONSIDER APPLICANTS WHO HAVE SUCCESSFULLY APPLIED ONLINE AND COMPLETED OUR ASSESSMENTS. <br>
<br>
For more information, you can also call us at 818-649-7556.<br>
<br>
At Whelan, we value people and we value relationships.<br>
<br>
Extraordinary people work at Whelan -- are you one?<br>
<br>
CA PPO # 16344<br>
